timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 10' Gorres looking for Asante with the cross towards the box but Knighton is there for the save for New England. #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: NE Revolution
timelineItems.text: 21' #NERevs 1 Kickers 0 Not much in this one besides McCarthy's goal. Both sides relatively untroubled through the run of play. #RICvNE

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 21' Vercollone finds Davis IV. Davis IV takes a shot that goes wide of the goal. Goal kick New England. #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Match ends, Richmond Kickers 2, New England Revolution 3.

timelineItems.text: Richmond draws level in the 24th min and it's a well-taken goal. Yeisley's header found Davis IV for a close-range blast. #NERevs #RICvNE

timelineItems.text: 26' Yomby with the ball near midfield boots it towards Yeisley in the box but Knighton comes up with the save once again. #RICvNE #USOC2014

timelineItems.text: 27' Free kick New England. Tierney takes it and it hits the cross-bar and out of play. Goal kick Kickers. #RICvNE #USOC2014

timelineItems.text: 2' Nguyen with the send towards Fagundez for New England. Ball rolls out of play. Goal kick Richmond. #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 30 minutes gone and @NERevolution and @RichmondKickers are tied at 1-1. #WatchLIVE ->http://t.co/d2dNXzmkAP #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 30' Kickers almost came up with their 2nd goal but play was ruled dead as the ball was called out of bounds. #RICvNE #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 34' CARD! Yellow Card issued to New England's #14 Diego Fagundez. #RICvNE #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 35' Goal New England. Mullins in the box finds Neumann to put New England back in the lead. 2-1 NE. #RICvNE #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: NE Revolution
timelineItems.text: GOAL!!! A pair of 1st-round picks combine as @p_mullins_7 feeds @neumannrevs4 for his first pro goal! #NERevs restore their lead! #RICvNE

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 39' Goal New England. A mistake by Yomby settling the ball leads to Mullins scoring goal number 3 for the Revs. 3-1 NE. #USOC2014 #RICvNE

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 3' Nguyen gets inside the box for New England looking for a pass but unsuccessful as the ball gets cleared by Willis. #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: NE Revolution
timelineItems.text: AGAIN! This time it's @p_mullins_7 with the final touch, pouncing on a major mistake at the back. #NERevs lead 3-1 in the 40th min! #RICvNE

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 43' SAVE! Tierney finds Mullins in the box for the pass. Mullins slides towards it for the shot and Willis makes the huge save! #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers

timelineItems.name: Richmond Kickers
timelineItems.text: 87' Foul called on New England. Free kick for Richmond. #GetReddy #USOC2014
